      "content": "I think I get the difference now. So the VP attachment makes it an adverbial modifier for the verb, and the NP attachment makes it an adjectival modifier for the noun. How do these different ways of branching out in the tree actually affect the way we represent the hierarchy of the sentence? Like, does the depth of the tree change?",
